This paper is about benchmarking salient object detection and segmentation methods, which is a topic related to computer vision (cs.CV). The paper also discusses the use of machine learning models (cs.AI) and analyzes the performance of different models (cs.LG). Additionally, the paper mentions the use of evaluation scores (cs.IR) and the construction of large-scale data sets (cs.MM), which are relevant sub-categories in computer science.
